{"title":"中国雨花石","authors":["方竟成"],"dates":[{"year":1994,"month":2,"day":4}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国雨花石"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"方竟成"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夸父逐日倒下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"涌出一片邓林"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烈士的血"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使这个神话"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叩动东亚病夫的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"振奋穴位"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用１８４０年炮口的滚烫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用炎黄子孙的脉跳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用延安窑洞的灯火"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浇灌长江之畔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浇灌钟山的石头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石头听懂了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赤诚的嘱托"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石头不再是石头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从圆明园门楼的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"支离破碎中猛醒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个巨响"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"午夜传来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用我们的血肉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"筑成新的长城"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是石头灵魂迸发"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是石头证明"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石头城虎踞龙盘今胜昔的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灼灼之心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石头与石头相击"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闪耀起冲荡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山矮水浊的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不朽光华"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石头与石头相映"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"收去阴霾、枯叶和"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梦醒无路的忧虑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石头与石头相连"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是一方不可战胜的热土"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站起来的民族"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人高心清"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扬眉吐气"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石头就这样"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轰轰烈烈"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开天辟地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石头就这样"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不再是石头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是红色的纪念"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是慷慨激昂前仆后继"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是热血写春秋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是一簇伟大的花朵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国的掌心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因此总放着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一枚光彩照人间的石头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它的名字叫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雨——花——石"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}